Westlake Chemical Corp (WLK) Shareholder Balyasny Asset Management LLC Has Trimmed Its Position by $15.82 Million as Stock Rose

July 20, 2017 - By Dolores Ford

Investors sentiment increased to 0.93 in Q4 2016. Its up 0.18, from 0.75 in 2016Q3. It improved, as 41 investors sold WLK shares while 71 reduced holdings. 49 funds opened positions while 55 raised stakes. 35.89 million shares or 1.17% more from 35.47 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. State Of Tennessee Treasury Department has 87,300 shares. Royal Financial Bank Of Canada holds 0% in Westlake Chemical Corporation (NYSE:WLK) or 5,077 shares. Riverhead Capital Mngmt Limited Liability Company owns 39,300 shares for 0.14% of their portfolio. Glob X Management Limited Liability Corp accumulated 4,707 shares or 0.01% of the stock. Kennedy Cap Mngmt has invested 0.12% in Westlake Chemical Corporation (NYSE:WLK). Ubs Asset Management Americas Inc, a Illinois-based fund reported 13,479 shares. Ameritas Investment Prtn Inc stated it has 0.02% in Westlake Chemical Corporation (NYSE:WLK). Evercore Wealth Mngmt Ltd Limited Liability Company, a New York-based fund reported 515 shares. Sg Americas Secs Ltd holds 0% or 6,517 shares. Northern Tru holds 0% of its portfolio in Westlake Chemical Corporation (NYSE:WLK) for 197,657 shares. State Board Of Administration Of Florida Retirement Systems owns 52,369 shares for 0.01% of their portfolio. Susquehanna Gru Ltd Liability Partnership holds 0% of its portfolio in Westlake Chemical Corporation (NYSE:WLK) for 10,400 shares. Keybank National Association Oh, Ohio-based fund reported 17,625 shares. Wedge Mngmt L LP Nc invested in 0.08% or 148,150 shares. Korea Invest reported 81,000 shares or 0.02% of all its holdings.
Since March 1, 2017, it had 0 insider buys, and 3 selling transactions for $1.72 million activity. Buesinger Robert F. had sold 8,193 shares worth $542,786 on Wednesday, March 1. $409,198 worth of Westlake Chemical Corporation (NYSE:WLK) was sold by Mangieri George J on Wednesday, May 17. 12,000 shares were sold by Bender Mark Steven, worth $771,785.






