About Allied World Assurance Company Holdings Ltd.
1001-5000 EmployeesBased in Zug/Baar, Switzerland

Visit website


Allied World Assurance Company Holdings, AG operates as a specialty insurance and reinsurance company in Bermuda, Hong Kong, Ireland, Singapore, Switzerland, the United Kingdom, and the United States. It offers casualty insurance products that provide coverage for specialty type risks, such as professional liability, environmental liability, product liability, healthcare liability risks, and commercial general liability products, as well as professional liability products, including policies covering directors and officers, employment practices, and fiduciary liability insurance.
Ticker:AWHExchange:NYSE (See More NYSE Companies)Industry:Property & Casualty Insurance (See More Property & Casualty Insurance Companies)Sector:Financial (See More Financial Companies)


